and our revenue doubled year over year for a few years in a row, and so we were growing

00:24:35.400 --> 00:24:42.439
our customer base significantly, and that became kind of challenging going from just a few monitors

00:24:42.439 --> 00:24:45.959
to all of a sudden we need this whole ecosystem. So, I'll just kind of walk you through that

