00:27:17.640 --> 00:27:22.359
the right refresh cadence and how do we send alerts and so forth. So, perhaps it looks like

00:27:22.359 --> 00:27:28.119
this where you get a new client and the account manager comes and says, we need to monitor

00:27:28.119 --> 00:27:35.880
Cocoa inputs and the Bad Egg model scores for this new client Wonka, Willie Wonka. He's our

00:27:35.880 --> 00:27:41.880
