00:34:18.360 --> 00:34:23.320
anything, but because each client has different needs based on their business, you're probably

00:34:23.320 --> 00:34:27.399
just going to end up with a mess of alerts, and this becomes overwhelming. You get a lot of false

00:34:27.399 --> 00:34:31.560
positives. You get a lot of alert fatigue, which just means people are just going to stop reading

00:34:31.560 --> 00:34:37.320
