01:11:01.879 --> 01:11:07.000
those new parameters. And those all kind of live together in the same piece of content with a

01:11:07.000 --> 01:11:13.560
drop-down menu where you can go and select which variant you want to view. And I think there's a

01:11:13.560 --> 01:11:18.759
